data.description: EVERYTHING ON YOUR WISH LIST INCLUDING A BRAND NEW TILE ROOF AND MANSARD CAGE! Stunning and Meticulously Maintained Lakefront David Weekley 5 Bedroom 3 1/2 Bath Estate Home in the Resort Community of Sandoval is the definition of laid back Luxury living. Over 3300 sq ft on almost 1/3 of an acre with Two Primary Suites and two guest bedrooms on lower level, Volume Ceilings, Travertine Flooring, Raised Panel Dovetail Cabinets, Stainless Appliances, Plantation Shutters, Pool Bath, and too many other upgrades to list. Step outside to your own Personal backyard Oasis. The Huge Southern facing Lanai with Saltwater Heated Pool, Spa, Tiki Hut, Outdoor Bar and a Brand New Mansard Pool Cage has a Wonderful View of the Largest Lake in Sandoval. No need to worry about stormy weather. Smoke detectors on alarm with Fire Department, Hurricane Impact windows and/or Electronic Shutters for storm protection and a WHOLE HOUSE GENERATOR helps to lower insurance costs and provide Peace of Mind. Agents please read the confidential comments and your pickiest buyers are welcome.
